{"tid":666012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏] 加拿大航空屈服中共壓力 將台灣列為「台灣，中國」","createTime":"2018-05-15T13:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T10:30:11.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"520e16ef1648e1a46f8227d7a60cf544aa6a8827","tid":666012,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:05:23.000Z","msg":"加拿大航空屈服中共壓力 將台灣列為「台灣，中國」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2426246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426246&d=bL7GQT81pL1CdRmlcKQKd%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0633d7d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426246&h=268b42bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2426246</a><br />\n<br />\n〔駐美特派員曹郁芬／華府14日報導〕加拿大航空屈服了。在中國民航局發函給全球航空公司，要求不得將台灣列為獨立於中國之外的領土後，加拿大航空公司的網路定位系統今天已經將飛往台北的航班列為「台灣，中國」（Taiwan, China）。<br />\n<br />\n在加拿大航空網站的國際航線特惠促銷票價中，飛往香港、北京與上海3個城市的航班都在城市名稱下方標注「中國」；然而飛往台北的航班，則在下方標注「台灣，中國」。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大航空屈服於中共壓力而將台北列在中國領土之下，已引起加拿大台僑以及加國友台人士的關注，表示將採取行動抗議加拿大航空的作法。<br />\n<br />\n中國民航局4月25日致函美國在內的全球航空公司，要求他們遵守中國法律在網站上涉及台灣、香港與澳門時不得標注為國家，否則將遭中國懲處。美國白宮及國會議員先後發表聲明駁斥中國的要求，白宮以「歐威爾式的無理取鬧」指責中國，並表示川普政府會做美國航空公司的後盾。"},{"pid":"51c8135cbb2d7eb9cf0db82ca13a7d568ca14519","tid":666012,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c8fe6c498e70039741df8ad82145699ddcfc3c","tid":666012,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:20:06.000Z","msg":"中華民國台灣省？"},{"pid":"b6fd91e0395c540f47d78496959a3d6726bcc340","tid":666012,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c8fe6c498e70039741df8ad82145699ddcfc3c","tid":666012,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:20:06.000Z","msg":"中華民國台灣省？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"鬼撚夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4947c03f26f6b8a3b50bf1142b043028c1a3472a","tid":666012,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"說好的Taiwan PRC呢<br />\n<br />\n又玩捉字塞"},{"pid":"4df4e8760301a5d8878dcdffd2f58aaaf5d97b0a","tid":666012,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/MibcIof.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMibcIof.gif&d=bL7GQT81pL1CdRmlcKQKd%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5b9d4c2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/MibcIof.gif</a>"},{"pid":"fd0f575b46a8f268d0ae3bd949fef1f928a3d6a4","tid":666012,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"加拿大航空承認台灣先係正統中國？"},{"pid":"7e2212cfc81387592211f05f7018cdef21035792","tid":666012,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"又係加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c82871d2800604e3cdc25ed3b822eb8fd365192","tid":666012,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:58:40.000Z","msg":"Republic of <span style=\"color: red;\">CHINA</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0568855d51d80718e7be1bd115de029ef39ed88d","tid":666012,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"支拿大始終係左膠國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b25e164da2ac8d3a7539fe43e79d8